snippet.title: Dick 'n' Dom's Hoopla!
snippet.description:
The HOOPLA game features a colourful array of stalls, each with their own zany take on classic fairground attractions: Dunk Dick and Dom with sticky stuff in Snot Shot. Navigate your claw through the traps to grab the right prizes in Grabby Grab. Try and make the characters riding wobbly crockery throw up in Plate Sick Spin. And knock the pesky Clown Kids down a duck or two in the Duck Down shooting gallery! 

Go and have a play! http://www.bbc.co.uk/cbbc/games/hoopla-game
